Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.04,0:01:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Dragon. He's a revolutionary!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys... What are you so surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a power trying to bring down\Nthe World Government directly now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the revolutionary army.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.11,0:02:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dragon is the man who leads it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:03:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I shouldn't have said anything about it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...forget what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're my grandson, I decided\Nnot to capture you on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give the Navy that good excuse,\Nso stay here and rest easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be an excuse,\Nso let's tell them that he got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came along with these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take your time and talk with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.07,0:03:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too casual!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more reluctant to say goodbye, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't seen your grandpa in forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?!\NAll you did was hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I still want my grandson\Nto love me, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That selfishness... You can\Nreally tell that they're related.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Its Name Is the New World!\NThe Fate of the Grand Line!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that old man was like a storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised about Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he was special to begin\Nwith because of his lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's out front talking to Coby and his buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to go?\NThey're your friends, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does bring back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it was Luffy who saved Coby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami isn't around either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she wanted to hear\Nstories about the marines...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she decided to let them talk alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to the pool with\NKokoro-san and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, to the Galley-La Company's\Nemployee pool that's behind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.65,0:04:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Nami-san's wearing a bathing suit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go bring drinks or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you guys also crossed\Nthat mountain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mountain? Oh, no,\Nwe didn't cross Reverse Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? But I saw in a newspaper before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that my grandpa's ship\Ncrossed that mystery mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and entered the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that article was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Coby! You shouldn't\Ntell him about it so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay, since it's Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How could it be okay?!\NHe is a pirate, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Don't just talk to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Let's see... This is top secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but headquarters' battleships can\Nget through the Calm Belt, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's not 100% reliable, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a swarm of Sea Kings several\Ntimes larger than battleships there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a terrible time there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,\Nat the bottom of the battleships,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they spread these stones\Ncalled Sea Prism Stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:05:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... That is to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that Sea Prism Stones release\Nthe same energy as the sea itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so to the fish in the sea, those ships are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea's energy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! So even when those\Nships pass by on the sea's surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Sea Kings wouldn't notice them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, they don't have\Nto go through the trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of passing through Reverse Mountain,\Nthe entrance to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can just enter as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy's scientists are pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got some good info.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady! Lady! Aren't you gonna swim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.50,0:06:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be quiet, Chimney!\NChances like this don't come often!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate lady! This is boring! This is boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! I'm eavesdropping right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that something you want\Nto broadcast out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dig into these epoch-making technologies,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you'll always find Dr. Vegapunk,\Na Navy scientist. He's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's really incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, Straw Hat,\Ntake Devil Fruits, like the one you ate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already clarified how\Ntheir powers get transmitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, another one of his big\Nachievements over the past few years
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.88,0:07:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is creating new tech that allows\Nan object to eat a Devil Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Vegapunk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... There are some\Namazing guys out there, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the world is full of incredible people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.39,0:07:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized what a small world\NI lived in before I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't come out of that\Nbarrel that day, Luffy-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I bet I would still be buttering up\NAlvida and doing chores for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you were on Alvida's ship!\NThat was really funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, the reason\Nyou were on her ship was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.32,0:08:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... Well... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to go fishing and got\Non a pirate ship by mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! What a bungler!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I was such a coward\Nthat I couldn't even run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But because I was on that ship,\NI was able to meet you, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't a mistake after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was doing chores on that ship\Nin order to meet you, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is, yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've kinda become strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.99,0:08:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being trained every day, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, your grandpa doesn't\Nknow how to go easy on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.57,0:09:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Vice Admiral Garp is a wonderful man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took us in when we had\Nnowhere to go due to an incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can train in Navy Headquarters right\Nnow all thanks to Vice Admiral Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, his grueling training sure is tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tough... but I really appreciate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll at least become able to\Nreturn the favor first, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm gonna get promoted\Nhigh enough to boss him around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Cool, split chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?! It's not split!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't get used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kokoro-san looking like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate lady! Let's play volleyball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you really going back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you have dinner with us? Dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Properly speaking, we're enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't become close, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san, do you know what the\Nsecond half of the Grand Line is called?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call the last sea that\Nlies beyond the Red Line
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by another name...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:11:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sea where those who will open\Nthe way to the next era gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who comes to conquer this sea\Nwill indeed be the King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.43,0:11:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Let's meet again there for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I see you, I'll capture you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get stronger and stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and one day... I'll become a...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...N...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... Ah... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm sorry! I-I got too full of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed! I wanna crawl under a rug!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got carried away, since I saw you, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.10,0:11:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna fight me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least get to that level.\NIt's obvious you'll need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's an Admiral we're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.78,0:12:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we meet, we'll be stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I am right now, it's such a wild dream
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that just saying it almost makes me faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, how can you\Nhave faith in me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.96,0:12:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're still a crybaby, huh, Coby?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.14,0:12:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that I was able\Nto see you two again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is a lot of work\Nchasing after these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get stronger and stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.14,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's meet again in the New World for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's go!\N--Ah, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys'd better be prepared!\NWe'll blow you away in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's see who\Nmakes it to the harbor first!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... didn't you just\Ncreate another crazy enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby is a man who makes\Nthings happen. I know that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was good to see that\Nhe seemed to be doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if he realizes how the world\Nsees what happened in Enies Lobby...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, an island directly under\Nthe Government was annihilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...although I guess the news that they brought\Ndown CP9 probably won't be made public.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it can't be made public,\Nsince CP9 is a secret organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, Enies Lobby caught fire\Ndue to the Buster Call in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and yet they claimed that Luffy-san\Nand the others did all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the entire military force\Nof Enies Lobby at our disposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of Buster Call,\Nas strong as an entire country's military...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... Why in the hell can't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.51,0:14:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...? Why can't we take a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:15:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from a puny little band of pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy should be protecting Justice...\NThere's no way this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.19,0:15:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just need to become a\Nbig shot and change it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, to think that he picked\Na fight with the Government
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to get just one crewmate back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how stupid is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're worried about Luffy-san, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that!\NI have nothing to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just looking on from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you two doing slacking off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahhh!\N--He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 1,000 years too early for you to fool\Naround in a place like this, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No meals for either of you for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Water-water meat barbecue is ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.95,0:16:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, that was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.91,0:16:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, say "Ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy! Water-water meat barbecue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sogeking! When'd you get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, guys, keep eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! The smoke is hurting my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how is it, Robin-chan?! You can\Ntell it was marinated well, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat! We heard that you woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Franky Family! Come here and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! They're having barbecue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! There are so many of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, add more meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:17:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Sodom and Gomorrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giants! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Straw Hat! You woke up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Galley-La is here, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you guys doing around the pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Shameless girl! What're you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pool, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... something smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san! No! You shouldn't\Nsee this! This woman is a perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.85,0:17:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking a break from building a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Rejecting a party\Nwould make me less of a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better have a seat for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.53,0:17:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! Entrant #1, Sogeking! I'll sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Party time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:05.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I was born on the island of snipers ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:09.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ I never miss my mark ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Lulu lala lu ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:12.28,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Whether it's a mouse's eyeball, lock on!! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please have these!\N--Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:17.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Or even your heart, lock on!! ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, guys! These are ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, help us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:29.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The man who hails\Nfrom the island of snipers ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:30.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Lululu, lulu lala... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there and listen, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aokiji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.07,0:18:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you run as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you could've escaped\Nfrom CP9 alone if you'd wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that it's different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.02,0:19:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't just stand by... and let them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jaguar D. Saul, the giant who\Nfought for Ohara 20 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was a close friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take pride in this attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still keep your head high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, I let you escape\Nthe island according to his wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm obligated to watch\Nthe rest of your life to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But after 20 years, you seemed\Nto have no tree to call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I judged that I could no longer\Nignore a dangerous bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that bounced around as it was chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above all things, I thought\Nthat you wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this whole thing, I was going\Nto settle everything regarding Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a matter of course, I couldn't predict\Nthat CP9 would be defeated at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you finally found a tree to call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether Saul letting you\Nlive was right or wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you show me the answer from here on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I intend to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, live strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohara still lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.01,0:21:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aokiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Robin! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you eating meat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing that stupid\Nstuff again?! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too! You're wearing a shirt over\Na bathing suit! That looks stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you tryin' to be Franky?!\N--Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.52,0:21:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the pirates are having a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally found a tree to call home?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.99,0:21:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is born into this world to be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right, Saul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.30,0:22:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Live together with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.04,0:22:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This way! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... I'll try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Do it! Do it, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do it, Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.86,0:22:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! You don't have to go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, but since I'm on an enemy ship,\NI used a bit of intimidation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop Ace, your second\Ndivision commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shanks Makes a Move!\NThe Linchpin to the Reckless Era!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
